"Where is every thing?" she ask as we drive past the corn fields. The fields are far. "This is it!" I say. She be shock. She live in a town. The store is near her home. She not see this much open space. I tell her about growing up in Ohio. She know who I am now.

We drive on a small road. We see a big hole with water. It is near my home. My home is in a small area. The houses are brick and white. Each house has a big yard. People take pride in their yards.

In spring, the yards have many flowers. The trees change color. The driveways have new cars. The cars are shiny.

My neighbor is Korean. He live near me. He is nice. He spend all day mowing his lawn. He sing while he mow. People laugh at him, but he is kind. He was a doctor. Now he is old. He mow with a big green machine.

My home is near his. Geese are in my yard. My dog chase them. There is a small stream near my home. It go into the water hole. I can hear frogs, the water, and cows.

There is a small area across the bridge. It is full of trees, plants, and flowers. I play there when I was a child. I build houses in the trees. I chase animals. There are always kids to play with.

Winter is cold. The yard is white. The trees are bare. When it snow, it is like a dream. I see snow angels and snowmen. My sister and I fight a lot. We throw snowballs at each other. We build forts. We play in the snow.

Portland, Oregon is a city that is different. Some people say it is "weird." The city has a sign that says, "Keep Portland Weird." This sign is on a building that sells pizza, drinks, has music, and is a place to dance. It is also close to the law.

Some people say "weird" means Portland is like it was in the 1990s. Then, it was not well known and not expensive. People made art and did new things. Other people say "weird" means Portland is a place where people are different and good things happen.

Portland is getting more expensive. More people from California are moving here. They build new houses. But Portland is still different.

"Weird" does not mean everyone is always kind. But it does mean people accept things that are different. Portland has modern things like stores from China. Portland has yoga, people who like to wear unusual clothes, and people who work in offices.

Perhaps "weird" means people in Portland do not take things too seriously.

My neighborhood has colorful houses. People grow flowers, herbs, and food in their yards. In the summer, people leave boxes on the street.

These boxes have things people do not want. They can be clothes, books, or anything. People find things in these boxes. It is like a surprise.

Portland is a city with many different people. Some people like to do goat yoga. Others go to watch soccer games.

Portland is a place where people try to follow their dreams. Some people drink too much at the bar.

Portland has a problem with drugs. This is a problem with people's minds. The rain and gray weather may make it worse. Portland also has a problem with people who do not have homes.

People come to Portland for help. Portland offers more help than many other places.

The mountains are always there. They are in the north. They see the sun each day. The sun rises and sets. No matter what, the mountains are there. They do not move. They do not care about my work. They do not care about my life. They are always there. When I am sad, I look at the mountains. They help me. They make me feel better. I like to look at them. I first moved here for school. The mountains were the first thing that I saw. The school has nice buildings and trees. But the mountains are the best. The town is nice too. There are many cafes. I like to drink coffee there. I also like to walk in the town. The buildings are old. The town is busy. But then I can walk to the library. The town is quiet. It is nice to be in both places. I like this town. I have good memories here. I have bad memories too. I walk by the ponds sometimes. I think about things. I am sad sometimes. I watch the turtles and ducks. I wonder about my life. I walk to the street. The sun is bright. The palm trees are tall. I see the mountains. They are always there. They make me feel strong.

If you go to Bensonhurt, Brooklyn, it is easy to find. Public transport is good. It is one of the ways people go around New York City. Bensonhurt is a city area. It feels like you are in New York City. When you visit, see the many Asian stores. 

Bensonhurt has had many Asian people move there in the last twenty years. You see Asian stores on every block. Many are supermarkets and laundromats. People like these stores. The food is good, the prices are low, and it is easy to get to them. Near where I am, there are four Asian supermarkets. They are all close together.

Bensonhurst has many kinds of people. There are immigrants and their children. The big stores are often owned by Asian people. There is a new park near here. It has ten basketball courts, a field for soccer or baseball, four handball courts, swings, and a place for kids to play. It has a water fountain too.

There are not many big offices in Bensonhurst. There are apartments and houses. Most houses are for two families. The people are nice but loud. You hear cars with loud music driving by. You might wake up to cars going fast. At night, be careful. Bensonhurst is safe, but people can be mean. You might see people who want to start a fight. I was hurt by someone here a long time ago. Recently, someone stole a package. People steal packages here.

New York City has a rule about dog waste. People do not follow the rule in Bensonhurst. You see dog waste on the streets. It is my favorite thing to complain about. Be careful and keep your shoes clean!

My home is on a big hill. There are not many roads for walking. People call the hill "work out hill" because many runners go up it. There are no sidewalks, so people walk on the road. The road is old and has holes. Some wires are falling down. The wires are old and broken. It rains a lot. Trees fall on the wires. People do not like the trees. They cut down many trees. They want to see the ocean. Houses are tall with big windows to see the ocean. The ocean is pretty at sunset. The water is orange. It is cloudy often. The sun is not always bright. Moss grows on many things. My car was green with moss after one month. There are not many children. There is a school near by. Most people are old. People have dogs. Dogs run in yards. Dogs go into houses if doors are open. Rabbits run around. Gardeners do not like them. Cats like to eat rabbits. There are birds, sparrows, hummingbirds, hawks, and eagles. There are no stores near my home. There are some restaurants by the water. There is not much beach. Rocks are fun to throw in the water. The bay is small. You can see the other side.

I live in a small town. It is in Tennessee. 

My street is small. It is in the middle of two big roads. We have a lot of cars on our street. But it is quiet.  Most people who live here stay here. They do yard work. They do other jobs. 

In the winter, we slide down a small hill. We live at the front of our street. We see everyone. We know their cars. If we see a car we do not know, we watch it. Some people walk for exercise. Some people walk their dogs. Kids ride bikes.

We work from home. There are four people in my family. My wife and I. We have two daughters. They are eleven and fourteen.

We play outside a lot. We play in the rain sometimes. We grill outside. It smells good.

We have many trees. They give us shade. In the fall, we have many leaves. We rake the leaves. We burn the leaves.

We do not have much snow in the winter. It feels like fall all the time. We use our back door a lot. We do not use our front door much.

I like to work in my garage. I work on my truck. When I open the garage door, I can hear the neighborhood.

It is quiet on holidays. Some families visit. There are more cars.

My area is in the center of the high desert. There is dirt, dirt, and more dirt. People who have not lived here may not know how it feels to see brown all the time. When you see a green lawn, you know that person spends a lot of money on it.

When I moved here in the 1990s, houses were far apart. Now, there are new houses. The area looks more like a city every day. Most places are changing this way.

Most people here are friendly. But like any city, there are good parts and bad parts. I live in a nice area with friendly older people.

The stores here are mostly big chains like Food 4 Less and Smart & Final. If you want special stores, you have to travel. You will not see Whole Foods here.

Many people in my city work in construction, I think. This city is not very big. There is lots of space to build. This scares me. I like things the way they are now. I left a big city and I do not want to go back.

I work in construction. I am a drywall and T-bar installer.

I like the animals in my area. People come to the high desert for many reasons, including the desert's beauty. The desert's weather and land make special places for animals. People should learn about these animals to live together safely.

My family and I like the animals here. I have three children. They love lizards and insects. They are outside now, trying to catch them.

There are some attractions here. Victorville is a good place for families to see the desert. The San Bernardino County Fair is here every year. It is a fun event.

You can visit Wrightwood nearby to see snow-covered mountains.

The Victor Valley Museum has rocks, fossils, Native American things, and old objects. It shows the history of Victorville.

My home is a college. I live in a dorm. My friends are my neighbors. The college has houses, stores, and a park. These are like a neighborhood.

There are three kinds of homes. First, there are apartments. Many students live in apartments. Second, there are houses for teachers and alumni. There are not many of these. Third, there are dorm rooms. Many students live in dorm rooms.

There are many people in my neighborhood. People from many countries and ages live here. Teachers live in houses. New students live in dorms. Older students live in apartments. 

There are many stores. There are shops to eat and buy things. There is a park for everyone. The park is safe and clean.

I live in this neighborhood for ten years. When I first came, I was sad. I miss my old home in Riverdale. My parents moved us to Stockbridge for a better life. We had a new home, new school, and new neighbors. 

It took time to make friends. I made some good friends, but also some enemies. I know Mr. Glen and his children well. I also know Dennis. They are like family to me. 

I went to Mr. Glen's wedding. It was fun. I caught the strap from his new wife! I hope his daughter Marsharii is doing well.

This neighborhood is like a maze. I use a GPS to explore. I go to the park to enjoy nature. It makes me feel calm. 

I also like to play with my wooden sword. There is a basketball court and a tennis court. I used to play tennis with my dad and my friend. We had fun.

I have had many happy times in this neighborhood. There are many more stories to tell!

My home is near the college. I like living there. There are many apartment buildings. There are some restaurants and bars. They are not very expensive. One bar changed its name. It is more expensive. The drinks are good. Most people are kind. They are students or have low money. There are many children. There is a school near my home. I do not know my neighbors. They smoke a lot. The building manager put air freshener near their door. It is funny. The buildings are old. Some are new, but they are not good. They are expensive to rent. The university is near. The manager can charge more. 

There is a restaurant near my home. It is cheap. The food is on paper plates. It is mostly cooked in a microwave. Across from the restaurant is a gas station. People say it is not a good place to work. The road was new last summer. There is a sidewalk, grass, and trees. The area is better.

My building has many trees. There are some stumps. There are more trees near my home. Behind my building is a row of trees. Then there are more apartments. I live on 42nd street. Behind my building is 43rd street. It is not as nice. The sidewalks are bad. The buildings look old. There are many trees. They hide the buildings. 


There is crime in my area. It happens at some apartment buildings. I cannot blame them. There are other buildings with crime. I like where I live. It is affordable. There are shops and things near my home. I like that the university is near. There are buses to go to stores and downtown.

My house is on a small road. The houses are close but look like they are alone. They are all yellow with white doors and green roofs. Many people in the neighborhood know each other. We talk in the evening. Small kids play in the street. This is good. It is nice to be away from computers. It feels like the past. We live near trees and fields. The sky is blue with white clouds. 

There was a storm last night. We got a warning about a tornado. We heard a loud sound. We had to go to a safe place. I went to the bathroom with my small dog, my purse, and some pillows. My big dog stayed in the living room and barked. Big hail fell on the ground. After the storm, the road was hot. The hail melted. The sun came out and it rained. There was a rainbow. I took a picture. My friends and family liked it.

After the storm, people came home. It was like nothing happened. People cooked and children played. I like this neighborhood. I moved here from another place. I like how people talk here. My house has two bedrooms and two bathrooms. All the houses look the same outside. But inside they are different. Some are small.

I like to walk to a field behind my house. There is a pond there. I see deer. I hear a big frog sing in the morning. It is a good place to live. It is near a city, but it feels like a village. There is a donkey on a farm. I hear it at night. I am happy to live here.

I come to this area when I am in eighth grade. It is hard to make friends at first. But I make friends with two men. One man lives two houses from me. The other man lives on my street. They do not live here now, but I still remember them. The same people live here now as when I first come. My area is like other areas in America. There are many two-story homes.

On warm days, I hear children play outside. The area is quiet most days. I have never had a problem with people here. People are alone here unless they need help. I have had things sent to me. I have never had a problem. I trust my neighbors.

There is a park near my home. I have many memories there. I play basketball, football, and baseball with other men. I have a bad memory there too. I was hit in the nose playing football. But the good memories are better. Now I go to the park with my cousin's children. They are young and like to play on swings and slides. Just thinking about the park makes them happy. The park makes me remember things.

My area has many different kinds of food. You can find Chinese, Indian, Mexican, and Italian food nearby. Many people use apps to get food delivered. People like fast food. There are many pizza places. There are stores with everything you need. There are dry cleaning places. There are Walgreens and CVS stores. There is a Jewel-Osco grocery store. Some stores are different. There is an Indian store for Indian food.

I like my area. I see bad things happen to people in other areas. I am happy to live here.

My town is small. It is in South Carolina. It is not special, but it is good for farms. The town is called Johnston. People call it the Peach Capital of the World. The town has many peach trees and cows. 

Houses are far apart. Most houses are two floors tall. They have metal roofs or gray roofs. Houses are not near the road. They are back from the road.

The town has one stop light. There are three stores that sell food. There is a Chinese restaurant, a Mexican restaurant, and a burger place. There used to be a pizza place, but it closed.

There is a small store that sells medicine. It is called Maxwell and Halford Drug. They are known for selling Cherry Coca-Cola. There is a grocery store called IGA. It is small and expensive. Many people go to a bigger store in another town to buy food. The most popular store is Dollar General. It sells many things.

There is a store that sells furniture. It is called Possibilities Furniture & More. It has been in the town for a long time. They have two people who deliver furniture. There is a pet store next to the furniture store. It is called Clark's Cuts and Kennels.

There is a doctor's office and a place for animals to see a doctor. There is a small school for young children. 

There are no parks in town, but they are building one. There are not many things to do in the town. There are no movies, bowling, or playgrounds.

The town is very small. You might not see it if you drive by. But it is a nice place.

I first hear of my place on a podcast. The podcast is about people who are missing. This is a surprise. Many apartments in this area cost over one thousand dollars each month. I never hear of this story. My friends also do not hear of it. Maybe people are struggling. I know some friends who cry at night. Things are expensive. We learn to save money. You like old toys and old clothes from stores. You smell less as you grow older. You might smoke. You might just get used to things. But the old store is always there. The smell of being an adult is old magazines on a closed piano. This smell is in the leather. It stays even after you wash it. There are three used clothing stores near me. If you start at the far store, you can visit two stores that help people in need, a library, a store with old books, and a store with strange things. The city center is crowded. Cars and people fill the streets every day. But you don't hear it in the used clothing stores. No matter how many people or cars pass, the stores are quiet. It is a good place to spend an afternoon. Every year, there are more cars and people. The city is growing. A large company that sells things online is here. It is still growing. It reminds me of New York. Everyone has their own goals. People do not ask much from you. You can be alone and quiet. People will leave you alone. It is not like the South where being worried means you care. People do not ask about your life here. You can keep to yourself. The city is busy but calm. There is always music. My neighbor plays the piano. People sing upstairs. We are like a group of friends. We help each other. We celebrate birthdays and funerals. I am lucky to be here. I like my neighbors. They treat me well. I clean up after myself. I share food with them. They do the same. We bring each other mail. It is nice to see them. I think they like me. I live in a big building, but my neighbors make me feel good.

I live in a suburb. It is like many other suburbs. There is a homeowner's association. The houses are all the same. They are single family homes. The yards are small. There are lawns, rocks, and short driveways.  There are trees in some yards.  Every house has a two car garage. The roads are new and good. There are no holes. Most houses are one story. Some houses are two stories.  We do not have mailboxes in front of each house. There are mailboxes at the end of the street. Everyone has a key. There are also big boxes for packages. The homeowner's association likes things to be the same. My house is near a city. My neighborhood is part suburb, part country. There is much land. There are pools for the people who live here. There are also walking trails. People can walk their dogs or go for a walk. The neighborhood is big. People can run around it. Most people here are old. It is a safe place. People look out for each other. There are also some middle-aged and young people here. The city is big. It feels small. It has many stores. There is one mall. It is not big. It takes fifteen minutes to drive to the mall. There are many stores to choose from. There are stores for rich people and stores for people who want to save money. My neighborhood is safe and nice. We have pools and trails. We are not near stores, but we can drive to stores.

I live in a small town. It is near a big city. My house is near the edge of town. Many people here have low incomes. But it is a nice place to live. My neighbors are kind. They say hello when I see them. There is some crime here, but not a lot. A few years ago, a man was killed near a bar. My family has not been hurt. Some things have gone missing from our porch.

Our town has a drug problem. Many people use drugs called opioids. Some people have died. There are groups that help people stop using drugs. My son goes to school here. The teachers are good. He has friends at school. The school gives free food to all the students. No one is treated badly because they are poor.

The town government has made the town look nicer. They have fixed roads and parks. Most of the new things are near the center of town. My part of town needs work.

I like living here. The people are nice. The schools are good. There are stores to buy things. My house is not worth much, but it is nice. We have lived here a long time. We like it here.

My area have much culture. It is on a hill, with old houses. I live in a big apartment. It is across from a old theater. Near my home is a small bar. Many people go there at night. A few blocks away is a big park. It has stairs and walls. In winter, some people live in tents near the park. It rains a lot in winter. They stay close to stay warm. They can go to a family center nearby.

I like my city. It has old buildings and hills. But I like the people most. Hilltop was bad in the past. The police were there a lot. People remember this. They work hard to keep the area clean. Some people say not to walk there at night if you are white. I think this is old thinking. Maybe people like me because I look different. 

Hilltop shows me that people can be mean. They make judgments. But Hilltop also shows me good things. I feel safe there. People help each other. I have met kind people there. They give me things I need.

I live in a small town in Michigan. It is a rural area with farms and small cities. There are no big stores like malls. There is no Wal-Mart, Target, or Applebee’s. If you want to go somewhere, you must drive.

My town is near two lakes: Lake Michigan and Lake Charlevoix. There are beaches everywhere. My neighborhood is quiet. The houses are old and different. Some are new, but most are old and have basements. Many houses have aluminum siding. There are houses of all colors.

Most houses have yards. Some have trampolines, playsets, gardens, and fences for animals. The people here work hard. They raise families.

You see children playing outside. You see people walking dogs, biking, and rollerblading. Neighbors know each other. You can tell who belongs and who does not. People wave to each other. The lawns are neat.

The neighborhood is not fancy, but it is good for raising a family. It is quiet, safe, and peaceful. It is a place where people feel comfortable.

There is a sheriff’s department, jail, and health department nearby. There is also a recycling center. There are baseball and softball fields. You can hear the games from far away. There is a small airport nearby. You can hear planes taking off and landing.

There is an ice cream shop nearby. You can walk to it. The downtown area is a short walk away. My children can bike to the park, which is eight blocks away.

This is a good place to live.
